{"tid":1798834,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭月娥: 監察海外媒體和反政府機構對香港示威行動的不實報導並無休止","createTime":"2019-12-26T13:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T14:34:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"472100d340a42b975792044d22ce0091936ae7de","tid":1798834,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"這兩天雖然是假期，但我們監察海外媒體和反政府機構對香港示威行動的不實報導並無休止，並即時發表了三份聲明作出反駁。那些言論往往是偏頗、不公道、不負責任、甚至別有用心。對香港近況不熟悉的人士，很容易會被誤導。我再次呼籲關心香港的海内外朋友，要查證事實，小心思考，而特區政府會不斷透過記者會、新聞稿、添馬台 Tamar Talk 等渠道作出澄清和反駁，深信事實勝於文宣炒作。<br />\n<br />\n12月25日聲明：政府反駁香港觀察指控<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/25/P2019122500693.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F25%2FP2019122500693.htm&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=2d0b82db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/25/P2019122500693.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n12月26日聲明：香港堅定維護自由及人權<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/26/P2019122600592.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F26%2FP2019122600592.htm&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=45d85f79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/26/P2019122600592.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n12月26日聲明：政府反駁偏頗及誤導的指控<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/26/P2019122600566.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F26%2FP2019122600566.htm&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=6c9e898e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/26/P2019122600566.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n#重要聲明 #林鄭月娥 #CarrieLam"},{"pid":"6f930a084d08b8a9d538897822897fab9b911083","tid":1798834,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a